article.description: — David Sloan scored 20 points and East Tennessee State beat VMI 80-79 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Sloan scores 20 to lift East Tennessee St. over VMI 80-79
article.linkText: Sloan scores 20 to lift East Tennessee St. over VMI 80-79
article.story: JOHNSON CITY, Tenn. -- — David Sloan scored 20 points and East Tennessee State beat VMI 80-79 on Wednesday night. Ledarrius Brewer had 19 points and eight rebounds, Jordan King scored 13 points and grabbed six rebounds for East Tennessee State (9-6, 1-1 Southern Conference). Jake Stephens scored a season-high 29 points, grabbed 15 rebounds and blocked three shots, Kamdyn Curfman scored 17 and Tanner Mans 13 for the Keydets (9-6, 2-1). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
